{"type":null,"faqId":9725,"title":"荣耀畅玩版（g750-t01）怎样作为modem连接电脑上网","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span><span>1.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在主屏幕，点击</span><span> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>2.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击“<b>更多</b></span><span><b><span>…</span></b><span> &gt;</span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">移动网络共享</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>3.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">选择“</span><b><span><span>USB</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">共享网络</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">”。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>4.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">安装好驱动后（驱动程序可以通过</span><span><span>Hisuite</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">安装），在</span><span><span>PC</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">侧，右键点击“<b>我的电脑</b>”，在弹出的菜单中选择“<b>管理</b>”，界面会显示新的网卡设备。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30220\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30221\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">备注</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：使用</span><span><span>USB</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">共享网络方式上网时必须打开数据连接，否则无法上网。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\